run to I have called them.

156
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:07,200
So we find that Saul, of course,

157
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:10,440
his name during this particular journey will change to Paul

158
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:13,440
and we begin to see how that God has called,

159
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,839
he's placed a specific call

160
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:18,320
upon the lives of Paul and Barnabas.

161
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:21,720
And in the Holy Ghost, the Spirit of God says,

162
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:25,040
separate me for what purpose?

163
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:30,040
For the work where unto I have called them.

164
00:06:30,239 --> 00:06:32,480
The Hector family is doing what they're doing

165
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,880
because God has called them.

166
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:37,359
The Ballou family is doing what they're doing

167
00:06:37,359 --> 00:06:38,779
because God has called them.

168
00:06:38,779 --> 00:06:41,339
We could go through the list of all of the missionaries

169
00:06:41,339 --> 00:06:43,980
that God has privileged us to partner with

170
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,660
and they're doing what they're doing

171
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:49,739
because God has placed a call upon their lives.

172
00:06:49,739 --> 00:06:52,140
It's not good enough if mom and dad were to say,

173
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:53,500
hey, I think you should do this

174
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,619
or if the pastor were to stand up and say,

175
00:06:55,619 --> 00:06:57,299
I think you should do this.

176
00:06:57,299 --> 00:07:02,019
The reality is that God Almighty calls people

177
00:07:02,019 --> 00:07:04,420
to serve him in this capacity

178
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,779
and God makes it clear that he's called them.

179
00:07:06,779 --> 00:07:10,380
Notice it says, and when they had fasted and prayed

180
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,299
and laid their hands on them,

181
00:07:12,299 --> 00:07:16,640
notice this, it says, they sent them away.

182
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:19,459
The church in Antioch, the body of believers

183
00:07:19,459 --> 00:07:22,299
at this local church, they send Paul and Barnabas

184
00:07:22,299 --> 00:07:25,720
to fulfill the mission that God had given them.

185
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,820
We find that it says, so they, verse number four,

186
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:30,059
being sent forth by the Holy Ghost,

187
00:07:30,059 --> 00:07:33,420
departed from Solution, from thence they sailed to Cyprus.

188
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:37,260
