00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,260
Why?

198
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:56,380
For it's the Gospel that's the power of God

199
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,339
unto salvation, amen?

200
00:07:58,339 --> 00:08:01,059
It's the Gospel that we've been called to proclaim.

201
00:08:01,059 --> 00:08:03,079
And we understand that Paul says this

202
00:08:03,739 --> 00:08:04,720
unto the inspiration of the Holy Spirit of God

203
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:07,399
in 1 Corinthians 15, the Gospel is this,

204
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:10,600
the death, burial, and glorious resurrection

205
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,619
of our Lord and Savior, Jesus Christ,

206
00:08:12,619 --> 00:08:16,640
that he did all of this according to the Scriptures.

207
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,880
That's what the Bible says in 1 Corinthians 15.

208
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,739
And I'm so thankful for the Gospel.

